  "detailed_description": "Raioh is a retro style shot and bomb style vertical scroll shmup.<br>Weapons are three types of main shots and bombs.<br>Main shot powers up to 5 levels by taking items.<br>You can choose the difficulty level from easy, normal and hard.<br>Auto bomb can be selected. However, auto bomb is not perfect. It cannot respond to high-speed enemy bullets or lasers.<br>Press ALT+ENTER to switch to full screen.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554950/extras/8d0866528cd127d13716b92321f63f25.avif?t=1696582100\" width=342 height=620 /></span>",
